# How To Write & Comment MA Code

> The conventions, patterns, and rules for writing new MA modules so they
> don't need to be refactored later.  Follow these from the start and
> save hours of cleanup.

---

## Table of Contents

1. [File Header Comments](#1-file-header-comments)
2. [The Comment Voice](#2-the-comment-voice)
3. [File Organization Rules](#3-file-organization-rules)
4. [Naming Conventions](#4-naming-conventions)
5. [The Orchestrator Pattern](#5-the-orchestrator-pattern)
6. [The safeRequire Pattern](#6-the-saferequire-pattern)
7. [Function Comments](#7-function-comments)
8. [Section Dividers](#8-section-dividers)
9. [What NOT To Do](#9-what-not-to-do)
